highlights.text: Oasis has the most spots on Top Songs United Kingdom. “Don't Look Back in Anger - Remastered” is the highest at #38.
“A Little More” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs United Kingdom at #30.
“Mr. Brightside” by The Killers has been on Top Songs United Kingdom the longest, at 1687 days straight.
“Stand by Me - Remastered” by Oasis is the biggest gainer on Top Songs United Kingdom, up 43 spots at #147.
